    .section.section--tan
        .get-started
            h2 Let’s get started!
            h3 You're just a few steps away from beginning your new career as a birth doula.
            a(href="/user/signup").button.button--red Sign me up!
            small Still have questions? Check out our FAQ page or send us an email and we'll get right back with an answer.